  "remarks": "QDe.100. Associated with the Islamic International Brigade (IIB) (QDe.099), the Special Purpose Islamic Regiment (SPIR) (QDe.101) and Emarat Kavkaz (QDe.131). Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 17 May 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 8 November 2022.; Listing: Listed by the 1267 Committee on 4 Mar. 2003 ( amended on 25 Jul. 2006, 13 Dec. 2011, 24 Nov. 2020, 8 Nov. 2022 )",
